name: 03-Exploring Data
content:
Exploratory Data Analysis



Grouping based on OTIF Status

This graph shows job count grouped on the bases of their OTIF


Distribution of Eaches

Here you can see the amount of Average and Median Eaches Released by Customers


Density of Jobs by Eaches Produced

The graph shows the number of jobs (Job_Cnt) completed for different production bin sizes (Eaches Produced Bin).


Month Distribution of Purchase Orders received

The graph shows the number of purchase orders received for each month of the year.


Monthly distribution of Average eaches produced by OTIF status

The graph shows the average number of eaches produced (Avg Eaches Produced) for each month of the year, broken down by OTIF status (On Time In Full and Not On Time In Full)


Monthly Comparison of Average Eaches Produced by OTIF Status

This bubble chart visually compares the average number of eaches produced for orders that were On Time In Full and Not On Time In Full for each month of the year.


Monthly Comparison of Average Jobs by OTIF Status

This bubble chart visually compares the average number of jobs completed for orders that were On Time In Full and Not On Time In Full for each month of the year.




Monthly Average Jobs by OTIF Status

This graph shows the average number of jobs completed for orders that were On Time In Full and Not On Time In Full for each month of the year. 


Monthly Job Growth Trend

This line graph illustrates the fluctuations in average monthly job postings over a specific time period.
